<Body>
	<Title>上海一家公司70多名员工食物中毒</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008年11月18日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>据<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">新民网</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">信息</Denoter></Event>：</Sentence><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e2"><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">11月17日</Time>，新民网接到<Participant sid="s2">网友</Participant>报料<Denoter did="d2" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Time tid="t3" type="relTime">今日中午</Time>位于<Location lid="l3">上海亭枫公路3168号的顶新箱包公司</Location>中，有<Participant sid="s3,s4,s5">70多名员工</Participant><Denoter did="d3" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e4">被<Denoter did="d4" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l4">医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e5"><Denoter did="d5" type="operation">治疗</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e6">其中<Participant sid="s6">1人</Participant>有<Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">生命危险</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
    
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7">新民网记者</Participant><Denoter did="d7" type="movement">前往</Denoter>食物中毒工人所在的<Location lid="l7" type="destination">金山中心医院</Location>里</Event><Event eid="e8"><Denoter did="d8" type="perception">看到</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">有人</Participant>在<Denoter did="d9" type="action">呕吐</Denoter></Event>，并获悉，<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="relTime">今日中午</Time>顶新箱包公司的<Participant sid="s10">70多位员工</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="action">吃</Denoter>了外订的<Object oid="o10">盒饭</Object>后</Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Time tid="t11" type="relTime">下午3时左右</Time>陆续<Participant sid="s11">有人</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>呕吐腹泻<Object oid="o11">症状</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e12">被<Denoter did="d12" type="movement">送往</Denoter>了<Location lid="l12" type="destination">金山朱泾地段医院</Location></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>随后，<Event eid="e13">因有<Participant sid="s13">42名员工</Participant>的病情比较严重，被<Denoter did="d13" type="movement">转入</Denoter>了<Location lid="l13" type="destination">金山中心医院</Location></Event>，<Event eid="e14">其中<Participant sid="s14">1人</Participant>有<Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">生命危险</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e15">据<Participant sid="s15">医生</Participant><Denoter did="d15" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">顶新箱包公司员工</Participant>中毒的主要症状为头晕、呕吐、腹泻，<Time tid="t16" type="relTime">目前</Time>正在<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">治疗</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e17">发生<Participant sid="s17">多人</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter></Event>后，<Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18">顶新箱包公司负责人</Participant><Denoter did="d18" type="statement">表示</Denoter>“不就是拉个肚子么，没什么大不了的”</Event>，<Event eid="e19">并<Denoter did="d19" type="action">拒绝</Denoter>记者的<Object oid="o19">采访</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
